	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D. in Christo.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reverende vir, en redeunt ad vos stipendiati vestri cum testimonio, qud honeste vixerunt apud nos, et nisi obstaret ista <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498">Germanię</placeName> irrequietudo, quam puto causam esse revocationis eorum, gratum nobis fuisset, ut sua pręsentia diutius adornassent lectoria nostra.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorati</placeName> fiat et qui rumores hic spargantur de motibus bellicis regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464">Gallię</placeName> et principum confoederatorum, illi commodius referent, quam vacet scribere in praesentiarum.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name">Sledanus</persName>, reipublicae legatus, a Tridento domum rediit; theologi autem nostri et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572">Wirttembergenses</placeName> adhuc manent forte usque ad kalendas maii.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Adversariis longe gratius fuisset, si prorsus nulli ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498">Germania</placeName> docti viri advenissent; <foreign xml:lang="de">so hette das concilium schon ein loch gehapt,</foreign> et ipsi, si diis placet, victores anathemata sua prostituissent.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Petunt nostri, ut omnes articuli ordine reasumantur, id quod et salvus conductus videtur polliceri, aut si hoc detrectent, ut confessio <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentii</persName> exhibita ordine ad normam scripturę examinetur.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Neutrum fortassis impetrabunt.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sunt simul in uno diversorio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572">Wirttenbergenses</placeName> et nostri; ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxonibus</placeName> nemo adest.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Philippus</persName> enim ultra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l361">Nornbergam</placeName> non venit et ad amicum quendam scripsit se non literas, sed et totos libros posse scribere de doloribus suis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pridie vigilię paschę venit heroldus <placeName type="auto_name">Zaberniam</placeName> a rege <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallię</placeName> missus et petivit parari sibi commeatum pro exercitu adventante; recensuit beneficia in episcopum collata a parente rege cum enumeratione ingratitudinis episcopi et posse quidem gladio et igne ulcisci idque iure accepta incommoda; sed quando<note type="margin">a.R.: °qm =quoniam?</note> adveniet in salutem et libertatem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germanię</placeName>, in praesentiarum se nolle.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic est status vicinię nostrę.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnipotens Iesus omnia vertat in gloriam nominis sui.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Amen.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale et saluta chorum optimorum ac doctissimorum hominum apud vos, cum primis <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quodsi posthac schola nostra aliqua in re iuventuti vestrę possit gratum facere, offerimus operam nostram.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorati</placeName> die progressionum, quę fuit altera pasche anno 52.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8374" cert="high">Caspar Hedio</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reverendo et doctissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, ecclesiae Tigurinę antistiti, meo maiori observando.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="author">[Bemerkung von <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ultima d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8374" cert="high">Casparis Hedionis</persName> <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentoratensis</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Vom gleichen Datum in E II 356, 892 (Phot...) ein Brief von <persName ref="p8374" cert="high">Hedio</persName> an Bürgermeister und Rat zu Zürich. Empfehlung der heimkehrenden Zürcher Studenten.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
